criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  adult patients, >=18 years of age;

  -  chronic hepatitis C, genotype 1;

  -  insulin resistance.

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  other forms of liver disease;

  -  cirrhosis;

  -  previous treatment for chronic hepatitis C;

  -  insulin treatment during prior 2 weeks;

  -  type 1 diabetes.
